Package: CMCR
Type: Package
Title: CoinMarketCap API Client for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("James", "Chapman", email = "james@paymenteconomics.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to access the CoinMarketCap Pro API
    (<https://pro.coinmarketcap.com/api/v1>). Includes endpoints for
    cryptocurrency and exchange metadata, historical quotes, global
    market metrics, DEX data, and fear and greed indices. All results
    are returned as tidy tibbles.
License: BSD_3_clause + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/James-Crypto-Research/CMCR
BugReports: https://github.com/James-Crypto-Research/CMCR/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    glue,
    httr,
    jsonlite,
    lubridate,
    plyr,
    tibble,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
